# Roadmap

This project is in early public development.

## Phase 1: Public Documentation

- Define the purpose of the toolkit
- Add workflow examples
- Document safe public modules
- Separate public materials from private creative assets

## Phase 2: Workflow Templates

- Add storyboard templates
- Add prompt organization templates
- Add reference image workflow documentation
- Add AI research capture templates

## Phase 3: Local-first Tooling

- Add small CLI utilities
- Add validation helpers
- Add documentation generators
- Add safe automation examples

## Phase 4: Codex-assisted Maintenance

- Use Codex for documentation review
- Use Codex for issue triage
- Use Codex for pull request review
- Explore safe AI-assisted development workflows
